IN RE: Lionel Dewitt NUNN, Petitioner No. 16-3105

September Term, 2016

United States Court of Appeals, District of Columbia Circuit. Filed: 11/18/2016 Gary Proctor, Attorney, Law Offices of Gary E. Proctor, LLC, Baltimore, MD, for Petitioner.

ORDER

Upon consideration of petitioner’s motion for voluntary dismissal of the petition for writ of mandamus, it is

ORDERED that the motion be granted and this case be dismissed.
